<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Uzbek Folklore ULTRA</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Segoe UI;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
background:linear-gradient(-45deg,#1a3c6e,#4b79c9,#162f56,#0f2027);
background-size:400% 400%;
animation:bg 10s ease infinite;
}

@keyframes bg{
0%{background-position:0% 50%}
50%{background-position:100% 50%}
100%{background-position:0% 50%}
}

header{
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
font-size:26px;
font-weight:bold;
letter-spacing:2px;
}

.navbar{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:10px;
padding:10px;
}

.navbar button{
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
border:none;
color:white;
padding:10px 15px;
border-radius:20px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s;
}

.navbar button:hover{
background:white;
color:#1a3c6e;
transform:scale(1.1);
}

.searchBox{
text-align:center;
margin:20px;
}

.searchBox input{
padding:12px;
width:250px;
border-radius:20px;
border:none;
outline:none;
}

.section{
display:none;
padding:20px;
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
animation:fade 0.5s;
}

@keyframes fade{
from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}
to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
}

.active{display:block}

.card{
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
padding:15px;
margin:10px 0;
border-radius:15px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:scale(1.03);
box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
}

.deleteBtn{
background:#ff4d4d;
border:none;
padding:6px 10px;
border-radius:10px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.infoBox{
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
padding:15px;
border-radius:12px;
margin-bottom:20px;
line-height:1.6;
}

.fab{
position:fixed;
bottom:20px;
right:20px;
background:#ffcc00;
color:black;
border:none;
padding:15px;
border-radius:50%;
font-size:20px;
cursor:pointer;
box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}

.modal{
display:none;
position:fixed;
top:0;left:0;
width:100%;height:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
}

.modalContent{
background:white;
color:black;
padding:20px;
border-radius:15px;
width:300px;
}

.modal input, .modal select{
width:100%;
padding:10px;
margin:5px 0;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>Uzbek Folklore ULTRA ⚡</header>

<div class="navbar">
<button onclick="openSection('home')">Home</button>
<button onclick="openSection('proverbs')">Maqollar</button>
<button onclick="openSection('tales')">Ertaklar</button>
<button onclick="openSection('songs')">Qo‘shiqlar</button>
<button onclick="openSection('info')">About Folklore</button>
<button onclick="randomItem()">🎲 Random</button>
</div>

<div class="searchBox">
<input id="searchInput" placeholder="Search folklore...">
</div>

<div id="home" class="section active">
<h2>Welcome</h2>
<p>This is an advanced interactive system for exploring Uzbek folklore.</p>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>What is folklore?</b><br>
Folklore is the traditional cultural heritage passed from generation to generation through oral stories, songs, proverbs, and customs. Uzbek folklore reflects the history, values, and worldview of the Uzbek people.
</div>

</div>

<div id="info" class="section">
<h2>About Uzbek Folklore</h2>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>What is Uzbek Folklore?</b><br>
Uzbek folklore is a rich collection of oral traditions that have been passed down for centuries. It includes stories, songs, proverbs, rituals, and performances that reflect the life, beliefs, and history of the Uzbek people.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Maqollar (Proverbs)</b><br>
Maqollar are short, powerful sayings that contain wisdom and moral lessons. They are often used in daily speech and reflect experience, logic, and народная философия.
<br><br>
Example meaning: unity, patience, intelligence, and respect.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Ertaklar (Fairy Tales)</b><br>
These are imaginative stories often involving magical elements, heroes, and villains. They are used to teach children about good and evil, honesty, and bravery.
<br><br>
Common characters include kings, poor heroes, witches, and magical creatures.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Dostonlar (Epics)</b><br>
Dostonlar are long poetic stories performed by special storytellers called <i>bakhshi</i>. These works combine music, storytelling, and history.
<br><br>
They often describe heroic journeys, love, loyalty, and national identity.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Topishmoqlar (Riddles)</b><br>
Riddles are short загадки that challenge thinking and creativity. They were traditionally used for entertainment and education.
<br><br>
They help develop logical thinking and language skills.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Xalq Qo‘shiqlari (Folk Songs)</b><br>
These songs reflect emotions, traditions, and everyday life. They are often connected to important events such as weddings, harvests, and holidays.
<br><br>
Music instruments like doira and dutar are commonly used.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Folklore and Daily Life</b><br>
Folklore is not just stories — it is part of daily communication. People use proverbs in conversations, sing traditional songs at events, and tell stories to children.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Historical Role</b><br>
Before books and modern media, folklore was the main way to preserve history and knowledge. It helped people remember important events and pass values to future generations.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Modern Importance</b><br>
Today, folklore is studied in schools and universities. It is also preserved digitally (like in your project!) and performed in festivals and cultural events.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Why It Matters</b><br>
Uzbek folklore helps maintain cultural identity, teaches moral values, and connects generations. It is an important part of national heritage.
</div>

</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Ertaklar (Fairy Tales)</b><br>
Stories with magical elements, heroes, and moral lessons. Famous themes include good vs evil, bravery, and justice.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Dostonlar (Epics)</b><br>
Long narrative poems performed by storytellers (bakhshi). They tell heroic stories such as "Alpomish".
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Xalq Qo‘shiqlari (Folk Songs)</b><br>
Songs connected with traditions, seasons, weddings, and daily life.
</div>

<div class="infoBox">
<b>Cultural Importance</b><br>
Folklore preserves language, identity, and traditions. It also teaches values like respect, unity, and wisdom.
</div>

</div>

<div id="proverbs" class="section"><h2>Maqollar</h2><div id="proverbsList"></div></div>
<div id="tales" class="section"><h2>Ertaklar</h2><div id="talesList"></div></div>
<div id="songs" class="section"><h2>Qo‘shiqlar</h2><div id="songsList"></div></div>

<button class="fab" onclick="openModal()">＋</button>

<div class="modal" id="modal">
<div class="modalContent">
<h3>Add Entry</h3>
<input id="text">
<select id="cat">
<option value="proverbs">Maqol</option>
<option value="tales">Ertak</option>
<option value="songs">Qo‘shiq</option>
</select>
<button onclick="addItem()">Add</button>
<button onclick="closeModal()">Close</button>
</div>
</div>

<script>

let data = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("folklore")) || {
proverbs:["Birlik bor joyda tiriklik bor"],
tales:["Zumrad va Qimmat"],
songs:["Boychechak"]
};

function save(){localStorage.setItem("folklore",JSON.stringify(data));}

function render(){
for(let key in data){
let c=document.getElementById(key+"List");
c.innerHTML="";
data[key].forEach((item,i)=>{
let d=document.createElement("div");
d.className="card";
d.innerHTML=`<span>${item}</span><button class="deleteBtn" onclick="del('${key}',${i})">X</button>`;
c.appendChild(d);
});
}
}

function del(cat,i){data[cat].splice(i,1);save();render();}

function addItem(){
let t=document.getElementById("text").value;
let c=document.getElementById("cat").value;
if(!t) return;
data[c].push(t);
save();render();
closeModal();
}

function openSection(id){
document.querySelectorAll(".section").forEach(s=>s.classList.remove("active"));
document.getElementById(id).classList.add("active");
}

function randomItem(){
let all=[...data.proverbs,...data.tales,...data.songs];
alert(all[Math.floor(Math.random()*all.length)]);
}

function openModal(){document.getElementById("modal").style.display="flex"}
function closeModal(){document.getElementById("modal").style.display="none"}

document.getElementById("searchInput").addEventListener("input",e=>{
let v=e.target.value.toLowerCase();
document.querySelectorAll(".card").forEach(c=>{
c.style.display=c.innerText.toLowerCase().includes(v)?"flex":"none";
});
});

render();

</script>

</body>
</html>
